edu.nd.darts.cimon.contentprovider
Class CimonContentProvider

java.lang.Object
  android.content.ContentProvider
      edu.nd.darts.cimon.contentprovider.CimonContentProvider
All Implemented Interfaces:
ComponentCallbacks
public class CimonContentProvider
extends ContentProvider

Content provider for CIMON monitoring service. This content provider can be used to retrieve information about metrics supported by the CIMON service, and data collected by active monitors. Clients may use the content provider to collect monitoring data rather than direct messages, or both. Content provider is read only.

Author:
chris miller
